title: [45w#73] [osu!lazer] 2020.603.0 更新日志
author: 45gfg9
txt_content:
osu!lazer 2020.603.0 [ruby=更新日志]Changelog[/ruby]
osu!lazer at GitHub
Release page

好巧啊 你也来水更新啊


Framework 框架
[+] Add missing System.Numerics reference for Android tests project (osu-framework#3598) author: bdach
[+] 为Android测试项目添加缺失的System.Numerics引用 (osu-framework#3598)

Gameplay 游戏体验
[√] Fix cursor trail not displaying (osu#9182) author: smoogipoo
[√] 修复鼠标轨迹不显示 (osu#9182)

Multiplayer 多人游戏
[√] Fix chat history not being loaded for multiplayer matches (osu#9195) author: peppy
[√] 修复聊天历史不在多人比赛中加载 (osu#9195)

Results 结果
[√] Fix results screen crashing for beatmaps with no online ID (osu#9190) author: swoolcock
[√] 修复结果界面在谱面没有在线ID时崩溃 (osu#9190)

Song Select 歌曲选择
[√] Fix crash after using Ctrl+Enter when current ruleset doesn't have an autoplay mod (osu#9168) author: Game4all
[√] 修复当前ruleset不包含autoplay mod时使用Ctrl+Enter崩溃 (osu#9168)

Testing 测试
[√] Fix redundant override showing up in build warnings (osu#9192) author: peppy
[√] 修复冗余的重载显示构建警告 (osu#9192)
